# Windsurf Codemaps Directory

This directory contains codemaps for Windsurf AI assistant to better understand the Space Analyzer Pro codebase structure.

## Codemaps Included:
- main.codemap - Overall project architecture
- ai-components.codemap - AI-powered components and services
- analysis-components.codemap - File and code analysis components  
- visualization-components.codemap - 3D visualization and charts
- backend-services.codemap - Server-side services and APIs
- frontend-utilities.codemap - Frontend utilities and composables
- README.md - Documentation and usage guide

These codemaps help Windsurf provide better code suggestions, navigation, and refactoring support.